      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for someone looking for a parts donor. The exterior shows significant wear, including several deep scratches, noticeable dents, and clear coat failure on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has multiple tears and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, it requires immediate attention as it currently has a rough idle and a known transmission leak. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
