    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving just as it did the day it left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, original shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains in a pristine state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, featuring a smooth-running engine and a seamless transmission, fully supported by a complete, documented service history. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who expects a vehicle in showroom-ready condition.",
