    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just drove off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive! \u2728",
